{"tid":616231,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我係美斯迷都真係比C朗迷倒","createTime":"2018-04-04T04:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T00:01:34.000Z","uid":102938,"like":146,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"c33485535c27431f1cccff0da958193c2ee3641d","tid":616231,"uid":102938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:32:39.000Z","msg":"「個人而言」一定係鍾意美斯多過C朗，亦肯定覺得美斯比C朗更全面（個人認為）<br />\n但你見到佢地兩個一直稱霸球壇CARRY球隊足足十年以上<br />\n尤其C朗每季瘋狂刷幾十個入球（唔好同我講咩入弱隊刷數據依d廢話）<br />\n問心果句，有邊個前鋒可以穩定到咁？年年刷咁多？刷入球唔洗技術咩？<br />\n琴晚見住C朗果球驚世倒掛，我都真係要比超大手指公佢，真心好屈機<br />\n好希望球壇球迷真係欣賞二人既足球比賽與比拼，而非終日引起罵戰"},{"pid":"ce3257f600cca2bf803d5623db9c22d928ebd37b","tid":616231,"uid":94360,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:33:53.000Z","msg":"真球迷"},{"pid":"3d2e6f2f745d3dc3f03085a6db225547cae33b6b","tid":616231,"uid":18646,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:34:36.000Z","msg":"幾多盲反都係on99咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b00df7c6e28c52038e4bc95fc04b26f33ace02","tid":616231,"uid":18646,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾多盲反都仲係on99咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"832100ba8f15be64389d53003e8d615799085712","tid":616231,"uid":5649,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:35:08.000Z","msg":"根本最戇鳩就係小花同牙朗d fans <br />\n本身兩個都勁值得欣賞"},{"pid":"f31826dfb9ceefed3442208ea1c99244960d9917","tid":616231,"uid":57145,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:35:23.000Z","msg":"琴日牙朗真係反唔落<br />\n搶點依然一絕"},{"pid":"c189c1d4300c77de306148943c0aff65b85f625c","tid":616231,"uid":72046,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-04T04:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/04/123647_58da81164d4bbd38165ec6084dbb0a6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2